<i>adjective</i>: 예쁘장하다 [예ː쁘장하다], 어여쁘다 [어여쁘다], 앙증맞다 [앙증맏따], 아리땁다 [아리땁따], 사랑스럽다 [사랑스럽따], 미려하다 [미ː려하다], 멋지다 [먿찌다], 곱디곱다 [곱ː띠곱따] <i>adverb</i>: 고이 [고ː이] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>예쁘장하다 [예ː쁘장하다]</dt><br>
<dd>quite pretty; lovely</dd><br>
<dd>꽤 예쁘다.</dd><br>
<dd>Fairly pretty.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>어여쁘다 [어여쁘다]</dt><br>
<dd>beautiful; lovely</dd><br>
<dd>(옛 말투로) 예쁘다.</dd><br>
<dd>(old-fashioned) Pretty.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>앙증맞다 [앙증맏따]</dt><br>
<dd>dainty; lovely</dd><br>
<dd>규모나 크기가 작으면서도 갖출 것은 다 갖추어 귀엽고 깜찍하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Something being cute and lovely because it is equipped with everything necessary although its size is small.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>아리땁다 [아리땁따]</dt><br>
<dd>lovely; beautiful; comely; sweet</dd><br>
<dd>마음이나 행동, 모습 등이 예쁘고 곱다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's appearance being pretty or one's mind or behavior being gentle.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사랑스럽다 [사랑스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>lovely; adorable</dd><br>
<dd>사랑을 느낄 만큼 귀엽다.</dd><br>
<dd>So cute as to evoke a feeling of affection.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>미려하다 [미ː려하다]</dt><br>
<dd>graceful; lovely; pretty</dd><br>
<dd>아름답고 보기에 매우 좋다.</dd><br>
<dd>Beautiful and pleasing to the eye.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>멋지다 [먿찌다]</dt><br>
<dd>fine; nice; lovely</dd><br>
<dd>매우 좋거나 멋이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Very good or stylish.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>곱디곱다 [곱ː띠곱따]</dt><br>
<dd>beautiful; pretty; lovely</dd><br>
<dd>모습이나 색깔이 매우 아름답다.</dd><br>
<dd>The shape or color of something being very beautiful.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고이 [고ː이]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lovely; nicely</dd><br>
<dd>겉모습이 예쁘고 아름답게.</dd><br>
<dd>Prettily and beautifully in terms of one's outward appearance.</dd><br>
<dd>2. carefully</dd><br>
<dd>정성을 다하여 소중하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Gently with care.</dd><br>
<dd>3. in peace</dd><br>
<dd>편안하고 평화롭게.</dd><br>
<dd>Comfortably and peacefully.</dd><br>
<dd>4. perfectly; with nothing damaged</dd><br>
<dd>상태를 그대로 고스란히.</dd><br>
<dd>Just as it is.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>